          ],
          "parameters": {
            "width": 544,
            "height": 560,
            "content": "## WhatsApp number checker\nThis flow is meant to act as a WhatsApp number checker for a spreadsheet list. It is useful when you have a list of leads or contacts and want to prequalify which phone numbers appear to be registered on WhatsApp before doing messaging or follow-up.\n\n## Use as it is or integrate it as a module in a more complex workflow\n\n## Requirements\n- Google Sheets access\n- WasenderAPI subscription and `n8n‑nodes‑wasenderapi` installed\n\n## How to set up\n- Duplicate the sample Google Sheet and fill in your phone numbers under `Mobile Number`.\n***template sheet***\nhttps://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1K0ps-y9OVJ5L15dnOekIxxTwxvTa0zOQNwGDEFSrYYY/edit?usp=sharing\n- Install the **`n8n‑nodes‑wasenderapi`** community nodes.\n- Configure your Google Sheets OAuth2 and WasenderAPI credentials.\n- Adjust the `Wait` node delay if needed to avoid rate limits (currently set to 10 sec.).\n- Set your WhatsApp session and the target number for notifications"
          },
          "typeVersion": 1
        },
